item.title: My Crazy Weekend
item.description: So I’ve had a very busy past few days. Everything about my weekend has had to do with the sketch comedy group that I’m a part of here at college, called 7th Grade Sketch Comedy. Sometime soon I’ll do a deeper dive into why exactly I’ve put so much of myself into sketch comedy over the past 3 1/2 years of school, but for now it’s important to know that I collaborate on sketch shows with these people and we also make videos together.
